# Cursor Rules for hobbyrider

## Typography Rules (CRITICAL)

**Typography styles must only come from typography components.**
- Direct Tailwind typography utilities (text-*, leading-*, tracking-*, font-*) are FORBIDDEN outside of `components/typography.tsx`.
- Always use components from `app/components/typography.tsx`:
  - `<PageTitle>` for h1
  - `<SectionTitle>` for h2
  - `<CardTitle>` for h3
  - `<SmallHeading>` for h4
  - `<Text>` for body text
  - `<Muted>` for muted paragraphs
  - `<Small>` for small text
  - `<Caption>` for fine print/footer disclaimers
  - `<NavLinkText>`, `<ButtonText>`, `<LabelText>` for specific UI elements

## Font Family

- Only Inter font is used. Set in `app/layout.tsx`.
- Do not mix fonts or add additional font families.

## Code Style

- Use TypeScript for all new files
- Use Next.js App Router conventions
- Follow existing patterns in the codebase
- Use `cn()` utility from `lib/cn.ts` for className merging
